---
import { EMAIL_CONTACT_PATH, PHONE_HOURS, PHONE_NUMBER } from "../../data/navigation";
---

<div class="contact-modal fixed inset-0 z-[70] flex items-center justify-center p-4" x-show="$store.layout.contactModalOpen" x-cloak @keydown.escape.window="$store.layout.closeContactModal()">
  <div class="contact-modal__overlay absolute inset-0 bg-black/50" @click="$store.layout.closeContactModal()" x-show="$store.layout.contactModalOpen" x-transition.opacity></div>

  <div
    class="contact-modal__dialog relative w-full max-w-md rounded-xl bg-white p-4 shadow-xl"
    role="dialog"
    aria-modal="true"
    aria-labelledby="contact-modal-title"
    x-show="$store.layout.contactModalOpen"
    x-transition
  >
    <button type="button" class="absolute right-4 top-4" @click="$store.layout.closeContactModal()" aria-label="閉じる">
      <img src="/svg/btn-close.svg" alt="" class="size-8" width="32" height="32" />
    </button>

    <h2 id="contact-modal-title" class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-center">電話のお問い合わせ</h2>

    <p class="mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-center">
      まずはお気軽にご相談ください。<br />専門スタッフが対応いたします。
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <a
        href={`tel:${PHONE_NUMBER.replace(/-/g, "")}`}
        class="block rounded-lg border border-(--cta_tel) text-xl bg-(--cta_tel) text-(--white) p-4 text-center border-3 transition-opacity shadow-[0_2px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] hover:opacity-90"
        aria-label={`お電話でのお問い合わせ ${PHONE_NUMBER}`}
      >
        電話をかける
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
